title: Bamboo 21-Piece Insulated Picnic Basket at Bed Bath & Beyond
description:
http://www.bedbathandbeyond.com/product.asp?SKU=14366059
This picnic basket is as stylish as it is functional. The basket is beautifully crafted from a combination of seagrass, banana leaves and bamboo, making it perfect for the outdoors and a unique accent to your decor. Thanks for watching. Make sure to subscribe to the Bed Bath & Beyond YouTube Channel.
